ontent/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-3-scaled.jpg 1514w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-3-728x1058.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-3-768x1116.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-3-1057x1536.jpg 1057w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-3-1410x2048.jpg 1410w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-3-150x218.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eP.S. \u003cspan\u003eIf you are not a marinara sauce fan, this one’s for you. \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-98601\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-4-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"crispy sausage asparagus pasta\" width=\"1683\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Crispy Sausage and Asparagus Farfalle with Burrata.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-4-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-4-scaled.jpg 1683w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-4-728x952.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-4-768x1004.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-4-1175x1536.jpg 1175w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-4-1567x2048.jpg 1567w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-4-150x196.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1683px) 100vw, 1683px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHere’s how I make it!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFirst up, the sausage. I add Italian sausage to a hot skillet and brown it until super crispy. You can use hot or sweet sausage – it’s up to you!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI transfer the sausage to a plate but keep the pan over the heat. Into the sausage brown bits go diced onions and lots of garlic. These cook until they are softened and grab some of that flavor in the pan!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-6-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"crispy sausage asparagus pasta\" width=\"1721\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Crispy Sausage and Asparagus Farfalle with Burrata.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-6-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-6-scaled.jpg 1721w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-6-728x931.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-6-768x982.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-6-1202x1536.jpg 1202w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-6-1602x2048.jpg 1602w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-6-150x192.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1721px) 100vw, 1721px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNext, the asparagus spears go in. I usually cut them into thirds just so they are easier to eat with the pasta. These cook for a few minutes until tender. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll while that is happening, the pasta is boiling and I’m saving some pasta water. Don’t forget to save the starchy water!! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe sausage goes back into the pan. Then the cooked farfalle goes in too. I also add some pasta water and toss it all together.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"crispy sausage asparagus pasta\" width=\"1711\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Crispy Sausage and Asparagus Farfalle with Burrata.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-7-scaled.jpg 1711w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-7-728x936.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-7-768x988.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-7-1194x1536.jpg 1194w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-7-1593x2048.jpg 1593w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-7-150x193.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1711px) 100vw, 1711px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOnce the pan is off the heat, I pull apart the burrata and throw it in. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eA final shake of crushed red pepper is important here too! If you want it, you know. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/sausage-asparagus-pasta-10-scaled.